<b>Some Recent Papers</b>

<ul>
<li>P. Dhangwatnotai, S. Dobzinski, S. Dughmi, and T. Roughgarden, 
<a href="papers/sparam.pdf"><em>Truthful Approximation Schemes for Single-Parameter Agents</em></a>, full version of FOCS '08 paper.
<li>T. Roughgarden, 
<a href="papers/tcs08.pdf"><em>An Algorithmic Game Theory
Primer</em></a>, TCS '08 (invited survey).
<li>J. D. Hartline and T. Roughgarden, 
<a href="papers/burning.pdf"><em>Optimal Mechanism Design
and Money Burning</em></a>, STOC '08.
<li>S. Dobzinski, A. Mehta, T. Roughgarden, and M. Sundararajan,
<a href="papers/IsShapley.pdf"><em>Is Shapley Cost Sharing Optimal?</em></a>, SAGT '08.
<li>S. Chawla and T. Roughgarden, 
<a href="papers/nw-pricing.pdf"><em>Bertrand Competition in Networks</em></a>, SAGT '08.
<li>H. Chen, T. Roughgarden, and G. Valiant,
<a href="papers/cspos.pdf">
<em>Designing Networks with Good Equilibria</em></a>, full version of SODA '08 paper.
<li>R. Krauthgamer and T. Roughgarden,
<a href="papers/decompose.pdf">
<em>Metric Clustering via Consistent Labeling</em></a>, SODA '08.
</ul>

